query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_islands, 
       SUM(CASE WHEN nearbyAirports IS NOT NULL AND JSON_LENGTH(nearbyAirports) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_airports,
       SUM(CASE WHEN nearbyAirports IS NULL OR JSON_LENGTH(nearbyAirports) = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_airports
FROM island_guides;
